<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.5">
<l>varuntāta varuntavatta malarkatiriṉ cuṭaruṭampāy</l>
<l>varuntāta ñāṉamāy varampiṉṟi muḻutiyaṉṟāy</l>
<l>varuṅkāla nikaḻkālaṅ kaḻikāla māyulakai</l>
<l>yoruṅkāka vaḷippāycī reṅkulakka vōtuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being a glowing body of blooming rays, of a difficult penance, that does not suffer,</l>
<l>being knowledge that does not suffer, being made of the whole without boundaries,</l>
<l>being the future time, the present time, the past time, being care</l>
<l>for the world as one – how shall I exhaustively recite [your] qualities?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
